//      201         Underflow
//      202         Overflow
//      203         Multiplication overflow
//      204         Division by zero
//  300:        ERC721
//      301         Invalid Recipient
//      302         Invalid on-received message
//      303         Invalid tokenId
//      304         Invalid owner/operator
//      305         Token ID already exists
